ook has reproduced considerable information about camels found in Arabic literature and in the pre-Islamic poetry and also in later times. Based on descriptions in Bedouin literature, the author recounts their types and reproduction, their names according to their ages, their diseases and treatments, the names of their limbs and sounds, their types of walk and races, and prices.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3900,"template":"","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false},"product_cat":[15],"product_tag":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3899"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3900"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3899"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=3899"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=3899"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}